A photorealistic image of two young Asian toddler boys standing side by side on a small wooden stage, wearing traditional Bavarian lederhosen with embroidered suspenders and white shirts, their expressions a mix of shy pride and excitement. Soft stage lighting illuminates them from above, casting gentle shadows. The background shows colorful paper streamers and festive decorations in warm reds, yellows, and greens, slightly blurred. The cultural fusion of Southeast Asian children in European folk costume creates a charming, heartwarming scene of multicultural celebration.
